-- Iraq May Offer Land to Builders for 4 Million Homes, Vatan Says
-- B y   E r c a n   E r s o y
-- 2012-07-01T12:22:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-01/iraq-may-offer-land-to-builders-for-4-million-homes-vatan-says.html
Iraq  may offer land to builders to
construct houses as the country needs as many as 4 million new
homes,  Vatan  said, citing Iraqi Finance Minister Rafih al- Issawi.  The Iraqi government can give as much as 300 acres of land
for free to each builder in Baghdad or other towns in Iraq, he
said, according to the Istanbul-based newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ercan Ersoy in Istanbul at 
